episodes.title: Guiteau The True Story of The Sex Cult Assassin
episodes.description:
Uncover the true story of the assassin, Charles Guiteau, and his five years inside the notorious Oneida Cult in upstate New York. Explore the charismatic megalomaniac who founded the radical religious commune and how Guiteau's string of delusions—from failed messiah to rejected lawyer—culminated in the shocking shooting of President Garfield, an event sensationalized as "Death by Lightning."
